{"tid":2353874,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"事實係大部份人都樂見智能電話進入「唧牙膏」時代，iPhone同an機都會趨向intel CPU咁㩒用","createTime":"2021-01-05T05:28:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T13:11:01.000Z","uid":109923,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d3012abfbd74178fdfdc675d0e87d25d07013122","tid":2353874,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T05:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QZ62ts4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQZ62ts4.png&h=1deb2136&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2代i7用10年唔落後，唔玩3A game/剪片好夠用<br />\nintel唧牙膏10年，最終得到嘅係「神級CPU、好㩒用」嘅美譽<br />\n<br />\n所以我稱讚「iPhone唧牙膏=唔換新機=慳錢」先係大眾最主流嘅諗法<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HM3Hts5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHM3Hts5.png&h=54ff3f61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當然，「iPhone唧牙膏」不等於「Apple唧牙膏」，arm Mac代表住ultrabook/netbook/mini pc即將開啟一個新時代：超長續航+效能好"},{"pid":"6e852d33d3225f752bd5a0e0d5755692c8d09fc8","tid":2353874,"uid":121697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T05:31:37.000Z","msg":"intel唧牙膏10年，最終得到嘅係「神級CPU、好㩒用」嘅美譽<br />\n<br />\n2600k神級CPU、好㩒用同intel唧牙膏呢個行為唔係一回事<br />\nintel唧牙膏10年，最終只會俾人屌不思進取"},{"pid":"8f8a991ce14d408bd9810984071c39c2e48e4b66","tid":2353874,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e852d33d3225f752bd5a0e0d5755692c8d09fc8","tid":2353874,"uid":121697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T05:31:37.000Z","msg":"intel唧牙膏10年，最終得到嘅係「神級CPU、好㩒用」嘅美譽<br />\n<br />\n2600k神級CPU、好㩒用同intel唧牙膏呢個行為唔係一回事<br />\nintel唧牙膏10年，最終只會俾人屌不思進取"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T05:39:57.000Z","msg":"事實係，大眾就係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E1Oz38b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE1Oz38b.png&h=ed4fcf31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果過去10年每年單核效能勁一倍，每年加2個core<br />\n遊戲嘅multi core/thread就唔會咁慢先utilize到4c以上<br />\no